{"type": "article", "id": 2232, "title": "智能书签", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T23:22:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222258uf4BAioHbWhFXw7E.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">这年头连纸质书的书签都要智能起来了。你是否也是一个买书如山倒看书如抽丝的人？这款智能书签</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">Smart bookmark by </span><a href=\"http://www.companhiadasletras.com.br/penguin/\" target=\"_blank\">Penguin-Companhia</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"> </span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">装有一个小型感应器、计时器和一台连接无线网的超小型计算机的智，当书签发现你已经超过一周没有打开这本书的时候，就会自动以作者的账户发一条 tweet 并且 @ 你，提醒你该接着看下去了，并且会模仿作者的语气或者使用这本书里的梗哦。听起来有点 creepy，但是用在拖延症患者身上也许会管用。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135126wXLN13KsFu29ntcU.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"350\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54736842\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135126Pvq0waGtVBxcliYh.png\" width=\"640\" height=\"477\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7453125\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}